    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at the 9th level, when you would deal bludgeoning damage to a creature with your taijutsu specialist weapon, you can impose a Constitution saving throw by spending 2 <em><strong>Martial Die.</strong></em> On failed save the target is dazed for a minute. If they are already dazed they are stunned. If they are already stunned they are paralyzed. A creature may remake this saving throw at the end of each of its turns.</p>",
